    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed thanks to a dual-joint spring strut front axle and five-link rear suspension, complemented by a factory-equipped variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery through the corners. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the valvetrain and reciprocating assembly. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a clutch that retains firm pedal pressure. Finished in Alpine White over Novillo leather, this E92 represents a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-performance engineering.",
